          "message": "build: update snapshots before running assertion tests in mise-upgrade (#506)\n\n* fix: update snapshots before running assertion tests in mise-upgrade\n\nMoves snapshot update to happen before `mise run check` and guards\nthe snapshot commit against an empty staging area.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* test: update snapshots\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
