          "id": "9bdedcfcbda7e1f0c425fa31b5fb273096d75572",
          "message": "feat: additional mise config and idiomatic version files enabling precompiled ruby support (#487)\n\n* fix: change generated mise name to distinguish from user-provided mise.toml, add mise.lock\n\n* docs: misc code comments\n\n* build: stop all docker containers locally when cleaning\n\n* feat: support all idiomatic version files and mise config files in mise installation step\n\n* this enables the user to use advanced configuration (like forcing ruby precompiled binaries) in their mise.toml\n* also supported mise.lock during the installation step\n\n* test: ruby 3 compiled test\n\n* docs: note about no main.rb\n\n* fix: cache mise config file search\n\n* refactor: move railpack json config\n\n* test: yjit test and jemalloc on precompiled ruby\n\n* test: enable sassc and other common gems to make sure they don't fail when compiling\n\n* docs: add dedicated mise page\n\n* docs: pulling in the mise docs\n\nneeds more deslop effort\n\n* test: snapshot update\n\n* docs: deslop\n\n* test: update test asset name for mise.toml generation\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit",
