          "id": "6d9bcf4f4ea53fbf10a6fd07ab24d9966f28235c",
          "message": "fix(node): prioritize RAILPACK_NODE_VERSION over engines.node (#601)\n\n* feat(node): prioritize RAILPACK_NODE_VERSION over engines.node\n\n- Add regression test case to verify environment variable precedence for Node version resolution.\n- Add reproduction example for the reported issue where engine constraints override deployment variables.\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* feat(test): rename and update node version precedence example\n\n* Rename `node-subfolder-node-version` to `node-version-precedence` to better reflect its purpose.\n* Update `test.json` to allow stderr, accommodating potential output variations during version resolution.\n* Replace the README to clarify the expected precedence behavior for environment variables versus engine settings.\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* refactor: improve package version resolution comments\n\n- Clarify that package versions defined in `railpack.json` serve as defaults.\n- Clarify that these values are overridden by more specific sources like `package.json` or environment variables.\n- Update documentation to reflect that version sources are labeled as \"custom config\" to accommodate CLI flags and external config files.\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* feat(deps): add bun to idiomatic version resolution\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* refactor(mise): simplify version resolution logic\n\n- Improve readability by removing nested conditional blocks.\n- Clarify that UseMiseVersions now supports idiomatic version files and explicitly overwrites existing configuration.\n- Enhance variable naming for better intent representation.\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* refactor(node): adjust node version resolution precedence\n\n- Update node version resolution to ensure ENV-level configuration takes precedence over package.json engines.\n- Refactor node detection logic for Bun projects to conditionally omit Node.js installation when no dependencies are present.\n- Streamline Node.js package installation to reduce redundant configuration checks.\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* feat: add example test for Bun-only apps excluding Node binary\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* docs: simplify README for node version precedence example\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* test: add snapshots for node version precedence and bun examples\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* docs: update project documentation and test guidelines\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* refactor(test): merge node-bun-no-node into node-bun-no-deps\n\n- Remove the redundant node-bun-no-node example.\n- Consolidate the \"no node binary\" verification logic into the node-bun-no-deps example.\n- Improve documentation in the readme for the consolidated example.\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit\n\n* test: remove outdated snapshot for node-bun build plan\n\nGenerated-by: aiautocommit",
